data.description: This is a clean, three bedroom, two bath home located in Poncha Springs.  This property has a large fenced in backyard an oversized attached garage.  There is room for an ADU which has become an excellent source of additional living space and potential income in Chaffee County.  Inside, you will find a timelessly designed living area.  Walking in the front door draws you into this open space and straight to the sliding door to the back yard.  The kitchen is surrounded with wood cabinets and light countertops.  There is a large island for eat-in seating and extra storage.  All of the bedrooms are bright and cozy with carpeted floors and big windows.  There are two full baths and a separate laundry area by the garage.  Enjoy the incredible sunsets and sunrises from the back flagstone patio.  This is a nice fenced in spot perfect for privacy.  Poncha Springs is so close to all of the mountain recreation you can imagine.  There are plenty of amenities including grocery, wineries, hardware stores, and more in the town of Poncha, but you are only minutes from downtown Salida. This is a great opportunity for a full time residence or a getaway investment! Schedule your showing today!
